I built this dashboard to explore the Airbnb 
rental market across major US cities. 
The goal was to turn raw listing data into 
clear visual insights — from pricing trends 
to host growth over time.

Built using Power BI Desktop with a custom 
Airbnb theme, covering 15,000 listings 
across 15 US cities.

Features:
- 2-page interactive report
- KPI cards, maps, charts
- Slicers for City, Price, Room Type
- Custom icons and Airbnb red theme.
